###############################################################################

	#### TEST NAME ####
Mutual Exclusion Test

	#### TEST DESCRIPTION ####
Verify that AMDSMI only allows 1 process at a time to access AMDSMI
resources (primarily sysfs files). This test has one process that obtains
the mutex that ensures only 1 process accesses a device's sysfs files at a
time, and another process that attempts to access the device's sysfs files.
The second process should fail in these attempts.

	#### TEST SETUP ####
	### [sleeper] amdsmi_init(AMD_SMI_INIT_AMD_GPUS|AMD_SMI_INIT_FLAG_RESRV_TEST1)()
	===> TEST SUCCESS, AMDSMI API Returned 0, AMDSMI_STATUS_SUCCESS
