	#### TEST NAME ####
Cross-Process Serialization Test

	#### TEST DESCRIPTION ####
Verifies that AMDSMI_MUTEX_CROSS_PROCESS=1 (blocking mode) correctly
serializes GPU API calls across processes. Process A holds the device mutex
for several seconds via rsmi_test_sleep. Process B then calls an AMDSMI API
and measures how long it blocks. A wait time >= 3.000000 seconds proves
Process B was serialized rather than racing through concurrently.

